# No Git / GitHub Unless Asked

- NEVER run git commands (status, diff, add, commit, push, pull, branch, etc.) unless the user explicitly requests it in their message.
- NEVER run `gh` or other GitHub CLI commands unless the user explicitly requests it.
- NEVER create commits, push to remote, or open pull requests proactively.
- Do not mention or suggest git operations as a follow-up unless the user brings it up.
